    "There are widespread calls for advanced biological therapies, for AI drug design, and for generative AI in supporting regulatory and these tools?",
    "payment models for medical research in general.",
    "While most calls do not explicitly focus on protein engineering, this is implicit in some of them, and most remain broadly applicable to the development of protein engineering tools, especially in industry.",
